title: Cleaning the Filters: Dirt Devil Featherlite® Bagless Upright UD70100
transcripts: Two removing clean the filters turn the power off put the cleaner in the upright position and unplug the power cord remove the dirt cup and set it aside press in firmly to remove the filter cover and take out the filter cartridge for quick filter cleaning. You can brush off the foam filter tap the pleated filter on the inside of the trash can reassemble the filter cartridge and put it back into the cleaner. It is important to clean the filter after every use and replace the filter every six months depending on use for more thorough cleaning. You can rinse the foam filter and the plated cartridge with tap water. Do not use soap or detergent dry for at least 24 hours before reassembling the filter cartridge and putting it back into the cleaner. Visit our website to buy filters on line or call our toll free customer service number.
